1
00:01:11,039 --> 00:01:12,300
A red-tasseled spear.

2
00:01:12,520 --> 00:01:13,920
She's a Huadan singer.

3
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:16,200
Why does she have a weapon rack at home?

4
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,080
This place

5
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:19,650
used to belong to Boss Yun's old opera troupe.

6
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:21,539
It must be left over from then.

7
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:22,720
Boss Yun?

8
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:26,650
Yun Feiyan, who committed suicide last week?

9
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:28,520
This is Xiaotangchun.

10
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:29,880
She's her junior sister.

11
00:01:29,880 --> 00:01:31,940
The deceased is in full rigor mortis.

12
00:01:32,039 --> 00:01:34,320
She likely died over six hours ago.

13
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:39,520
The deceased is missing an earring.

14
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:47,280
The other earring is right here.

15
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:56,800
Judging by the wound,

16
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:59,720
it must have also been caused by a Red Tassel Spear.

17
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,320
If the weapon is the same,

18
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,000
that means

19
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:05,200
Xiaotangchun killed her father first.

20
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:07,560
And while she was killing her father,

21
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:09,240
they got into a struggle,

22
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:11,340
and this earring was torn off.

23
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:13,680
Then Xiaotangchun committed suicide.

24
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,360
That's not right.

25
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,040
This corpse

26
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:19,500
only shows signs of rigor mortis in the legs.

27
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,640
Judging by the livor mortis,

28
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:23,970
the time of death was about four hours ago.

29
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,840
You mean to say

30
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:27,760
Xiaotangchun died at least

31
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:29,690
two hours earlier than her father?

32
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:32,120
If it was the same weapon,

33
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,520
that killed Xiaotangchun first,

34
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,650
and then her father,

35
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:37,490
it should have been left on her father's body.

36
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,040
Also,

37
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:40,120
if Xiaotangchun died first,

38
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:41,240
why did her father

39
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,840
pull off one of her earrings?

40
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:44,920
Do you smell that?

41
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:49,200
It smells like osmanthus rice cake and millet porridge.

42
00:02:49,200 --> 00:02:50,730
Someone is cooking inside.

43
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:01,380
What are you doing?

44
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:05,960
Don't misunderstand, officer.

45
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,960
I reported the case.

46
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,040
The kids are having a hot meal.

47
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,080
We'll leave right away.

48
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,280
Did you find the body?

49
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:13,400
I heard opera singing in the yard

50
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,880
and came over to beg for some copper coins.

51
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:17,560
You said you came in because you heard opera singing?

52
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,360
That's right.

53
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:21,160
I thought there were many people watching the opera,

54
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,200
so I could beg for more.

55
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:22,760
Sir,

56
00:03:23,079 --> 00:03:24,240
as soon as I pushed the door open,

57
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,760
the sound suddenly stopped.

58
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:28,440
Was the singing still going on before you entered?

59
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,240
That's right.

60
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,520
Stumbling upon a suicide

61
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,480
is bad luck enough.

62
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:32,240
Wait a minute.

63
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,800
What makes you say it was suicide?

64
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,600
Did you see it?

65
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,160
Isn't it obvious?

66
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,680
Before I came in,

67
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,560
she killed the old one first,

68
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:40,840
then killed herself.

69
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,400
The point is, in this yard,

70
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,600
I didn't see anyone.

71
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,250
What is this if not suicide?

72
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,000
Unless...

73
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,400
it was a ghost.

74
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,920
When did you find the body?

75
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,120
Around...

76
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:52,890
one o'clock.

77
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:56,160
Wang's Wontons had just set up their stall.

78
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:57,480
Officer,

79
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,240
sir,

80
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,240
if there's nothing else,

81
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,560
we'll be going now.

82
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,040
Hurry, let's go.

83
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:06,340
There must be another murder weapon.

84
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:08,760
Whether there's another weapon or not,

85
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:09,800
Xiaotangchun's father

86
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,280
definitely didn't commit suicide.

87
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,080
We've got a big case on our hands.

88
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:16,160
The livor mortis on the victim's back formed first.

89
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:18,920
She must have been lying down when she was killed.

90
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:22,040
Someone deliberately posed her like this after she died.

91
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:24,560
That beggar said he heard someone singing opera.

92
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:26,320
A dead person singing opera?

93
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,840
That's impossible.

94
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:31,900
Then someone must be playing tricks.

95
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:32,920
Zhao Erbao.

96
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,159
Search this place thoroughly.

97
00:04:35,159 --> 00:04:37,020
Bring back anything suspicious.

98
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,640
Yes.

99
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:40,120
Follow me.

100
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:50,560
In the entire room,

101
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,480
there isn't a single valuable thing.

102
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,320
The clothes in the cabinet are tattered too.

103
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:56,000
With an opium addict in the house,

104
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,800
even if there were valuable things,

105
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,600
they've probably been sold off.

106
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,800
This rouge isn't cheap.

107
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:12,530
It doesn't look like something she could afford.

108
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,410
She wasn't wearing this today.

109
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,760
You have a dog's nose.

110
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:19,820
My grandma says that about me too.

111
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:23,220
Medical Examiner Qin.

112
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,220
Medical Examiner Qin.

113
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:28,040
Can you hear me?

114
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:29,080
I can hear you.

115
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,040
Where are you?

116
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,280
I can hear you.

117
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,240
Stop!

118
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:44,920
Are you crazy?

119
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,000
Get lost!

120
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:52,580
What are you doing?

121
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:14,920
Bite!

122
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:15,480
Bite it!

123
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,000
Bite!

124
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,040
Bastard!

125
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,760
You crushed my Black King Kong!

126
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:26,040
I raised it on incense ash from Hong Temple.

127
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:26,880
If it had won,

128
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:29,720
three of your lives wouldn't be enough to pay for it.

129
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,380
Incense ash from Hong Temple?

130
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,580
That might fool out-of-towners.

131
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,800
Did you see that?

132
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,920
Jiangbei insect dealers

133
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,520
soaked it in chili water.

134
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,050
Some 'Black King Kong'.

135
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:59,120
You trying to mess with me?

136
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:01,040
If you don't explain,

137
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,160
no one leaves.

138
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,090
What do you want?

139
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:04,360
How dare you sell me fakes?

140
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,160
What fakes?

141
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:06,800
What fakes?

142
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,960
You dare scam me?

143
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,280
What fakes?

144
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:10,340
Explain yourself.

145
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:17,840
Didn't know you were so agile.

146
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,240
Dr. Qin,

147
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,800
aren't you an expert on insects too?

148
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,840
Expert, my foot.

149
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:28,880
I just raided a fake insect den last month.

150
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,320
The deceased is Meng San.

151
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,240
69 years old,

152
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,520
unemployed,

153
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,140
a long-time opium addict.

154
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,600
So his social circle

155
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,520
consisted of people from opium dens.

156
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:43,580
The other deceased is Xiaotangchun.

157
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,720
29 years old,

158
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,920
a female lead in the Yunshang Opera Troupe.

159
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,760
According to the troupe members,

160
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:50,120
after Boss Yun died,

161
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:52,440
she had been mentally unstable.

162
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,720
She always said she could see Boss Yun's ghost.

163
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,650
We also had this cufflink checked.

164
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:58,680
It's a handmade mica cufflink.

165
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,930
About a dozen years ago,

166
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,820
wealthy families would use this.

167
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,600
Later, fewer people bought them,

168
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:06,000
so the craft was lost.

169
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,680
The scene was carefully examined.

170
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,540
No other murder weapon was found.

171
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,880
The window on the back wall of the troupe

172
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,740
has a clear view of the front door.

173
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:17,480
Someone must have hidden behind the back wall

174
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:19,040
and made singing sounds.

175
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:21,000
to make the beggar think

176
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,360
that the singing he heard

177
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,690
came from the deceased.

178
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:24,920
Bao,

179
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,400
get someone to find

180
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,840
the male Dan actors in the Concession

181
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:29,040
and list their names for me.

182
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:29,560
Okay.

183
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,650
Keep it a secret.

184
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,960
Come with me.

185
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:34,520
Let's go. Stop writing.

186
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,200
Let's go.

187
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,000
Put on protective suits.

188
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:46,720
Gloves.

189
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:54,240
There is a wound on the pericardium.

190
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:55,940
The incision is clean,

191
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:57,490
five centimeters wide.

192
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,900
It is a fatal wound,

193
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,720
but it likely wasn't caused by the Red Tassel Spear.

194
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,600
It was likely a

195
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:04,340
single-edged blade about 20 centimeters long.

196
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:11,160
The killer likely used a dagger first

197
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,420
to kill Xiaotangchun,

198
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,520
then used the Red Tassel Spear

199
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:16,280
to cover the original wound.

200
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:19,120
Xiaotangchun's time of death

201
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:21,560
was between 9:00 and 9:30 this morning.

202
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:23,360
And her father, Meng San,

203
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,520
died between

204
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:26,440
11:00 and 11:30.

205
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,120
In other words,

206
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:31,240
the killer murdered Xiaotangchun with a dagger first.

207
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:33,400
Two hours after she died,

208
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:36,530
the killer used the Red Tassel Spear to kill Meng San.

209
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:38,320
Finally, using the same spear,

210
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,760
they targeted Xiaotangchun's wound

211
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:41,280
to inflict secondary damage

212
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:43,080
and staged the scene we see here.

213
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:48,140
The scene must have been carefully cleaned.

214
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:50,640
Otherwise, there would be more blood.

215
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:55,080
The two victims died two hours apart.

216
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:57,770
Counting from the last victim's time of death

217
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,240
until

218
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,560
we found the bodies,

219
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,760
another two hours passed.

220
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:05,200
The killer had enough time

221
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,800
to clean and stage the scene.

222
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:10,160
Impossible. Impossible.

223
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:10,960
She is a ghost.

224
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:13,160
She kept shouting about a ghost.

225
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:16,240
Could her death be related to this ghost?

226
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:18,890
Let's go.

227
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:19,920
Let's ask around.

228
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:28,200
Here.

229
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:32,520
What is this?

230
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:39,800
Sheep dung.

231
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:44,920
I'm kidding.

232
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:47,000
It's pepper and mint.

233
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:49,890
Better than foreigners' smelling salts.

234
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:56,920
Why do I feel like it's actually sheep dung?

235
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:03,120
Thank you, Landlady.

236
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,050
You're welcome.

237
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:10,920
Did you not see me?

238
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,600
So you do know how to show up.

239
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,850
Isn't it a good thing I didn't come?

240
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:17,600
That means everything is peaceful.

241
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:20,000
If I came every day, that would be terrible.

242
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,040
Speak.

243
00:11:21,040 --> 00:11:23,170
What information are you looking for?

244
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:30,200
Got it.

245
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,240
Wait a moment.

246
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,000
That water.

247
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:36,040
My father and I haven't gone out all day.

248
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:37,640
I didn't know until you came.

249
00:11:37,680 --> 00:11:40,040
Did you hear anyone singing opera today?

250
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,680
I did. She sings every day.

251
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:44,320
My dad and I sat and listened for quite a while.

252
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:46,920
Did you hear anything else besides the singing?

253
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:49,560
It sounded like she was calling someone.

254
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:50,980
She was calling him...

255
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:52,480
Senior Brother, I think.

256
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,410
Senior Brother.

257
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,320
The names of all the men in the Concession who can sing opera,

258
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:57,080
I've written them all down for you.

259
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,010
Inspector Zhao.

260
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,560
Yun Feiyan's ghost...

261
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:01,920
was singing at Laixian Theater yesterday.

262
00:12:01,920 --> 00:12:03,850
Should I write her name down or not?

263
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:05,360
Bullshit.

264
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:07,160
Unless a coffin lid turned into a spirit.

265
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:08,280
Who told you that?

266
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:10,160
One of our brothers saw it with his own eyes.

267
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:12,560
Are you sure it was the same person singing?

268
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:14,440
Two people.

269
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:16,970
At first, it was Xiaotangchun.

270
00:12:18,040 --> 00:12:19,440
After a long while,

271
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,160
someone else sang.

272
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:22,120
Are you sure?

273
00:12:22,520 --> 00:12:23,560
The second person

274
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:25,220
sang much better than her.

275
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,170
It had Boss Yun's style.

276
00:12:27,280 --> 00:12:28,120
Boss Yun?

277
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:29,360
Yun Feiyan.

278
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:31,400
It looks like her.

279
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:32,440
Like Boss Yun.

280
00:12:35,760 --> 00:12:38,320
Yun Feiyan is a famous Dan actor in Shanghai.

281
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:41,560
She's been the top of the opera world for years.

282
00:12:41,880 --> 00:12:44,240
It was discovered a few days ago

283
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,880
that she is actually a woman.

284
00:12:45,880 --> 00:12:46,760
This news

285
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:49,320
has turned all of Shanghai upside down.

286
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:53,380
She dressed as a man for over a decade,

287
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:54,760
and no one found out.

288
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,320
If you ask me,

289
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:59,640
Boss Yun was just born at the wrong time.

290
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,960
In the past, women weren't allowed on stage.

291
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:03,420
It was all male Dan actors.

292
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:05,560
But later, there was Mao'er Opera,

293
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:07,080
but those were all women.

294
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,680
Until over ten years ago,

295
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,440
when the ban was finally lifted,

296
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:12,160
and men and women could perform together.

297
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:13,640
You mean Boss Yun committed suicide

298
00:13:13,640 --> 00:13:16,600
because of this scandal?

299
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:20,500
I heard that after it was exposed,

300
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:22,520
fans didn't blame Boss Yun.

301
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:25,250
Instead, they went to the theater to support her.

302
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:26,720
But she probably

303
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:28,250
couldn't forgive herself.

304
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:29,760
The play started,

305
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:32,000
and she killed herself on stage.

306
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:34,170
Regarding Boss Yun's suicide,

307
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,560
was it reported to the police?

308
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:36,280
No.

309
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:39,480
The troupe handled the funeral.

310
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,440
You don't really think

311
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:43,300
Boss Yun came back to life, do you?

312
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,480
They are all here.

313
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:48,320
The negatives of Yun Feiyan from the studio

314
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,720
have all been developed.

315
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,400
This is the outfit.

316
00:14:04,760 --> 00:14:06,520
The person who escaped in the alley today

317
00:14:06,520 --> 00:14:07,720
was wearing this.

318
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:09,680
You're saying the person you chased today

319
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:10,840
was Yun Feiyan?

320
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:16,080
That's impossible.

321
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:17,820
In all of Shanghai,

322
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,080
who doesn't know Yun Feiyan

323
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,320
died on stage?

324
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,800
I buried her myself.

325
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:26,320
Just based on this suicide note,

326
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:28,000
you concluded it was suicide?

327
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:29,920
With so many people watching,

328
00:14:29,920 --> 00:14:32,120
everyone knows she committed suicide.

329
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:35,040
Why was Boss Yun photographed like this?

330
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:37,720
She performed at private parties and drank.

331
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:39,250
She showed her true colors.

332
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,810
She has no one else to blame.

333
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:43,250
Boss Yun cared about her voice.

334
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:45,490
She never touched alcohol or tobacco.

335
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:48,280
What nonsense.

336
00:14:50,920 --> 00:14:51,720
Hand it over.

337
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:53,840
This thing is bad luck.

338
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:54,880
Why keep it?

339
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:56,810
Do you have a death wish?

340
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:01,640
Take him away.

341
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,080
What are you doing?

342
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:03,640
Let go!

343
00:15:03,640 --> 00:15:04,160
Shut up. Move.

344
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:05,160
I'll walk myself.

345
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,360
Let go of me.

346
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:07,960
Erxizi, run!

347
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:08,680
Wait.

348
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:11,680
Do you know whose house Boss Yun is performing at?

349
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:13,000
Number 6, Fourth Road.

350
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:24,640
Who are you two?

351
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:29,060
We are friends of Boss Yun.

352
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,880
Since you are friends of Boss Yun,

353
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:38,080
if you need anything,

354
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,010
just let us know.

355
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,720
We know Boss Yun didn't come here

356
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:42,380
to perform at a private party.

357
00:15:42,560 --> 00:15:44,020
So you don't need to worry.

358
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:45,080
Maybe...

359
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:47,080
It's better to talk inside.
